{"tid":1620091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[八字解疑難]救港救民 八字官非 身體健康檢查","createTime":"2019-10-04T09:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T01:52:52.000Z","uid":268450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f7aee3ccc5637c1868713f656e1669ffebf7abab","tid":1620091,"uid":268450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:25:35.000Z","msg":"睇到今日心痛香港人安危 只望幫得幾多得幾多 <br />\n<br />\n會唔會易惹官非 會唔會有無罔之災<br />\n會唔會扑到個頭 會唔會有跌斷手腳<br />\n邊個月要小心啲 <br />\n<br />\n放低你 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">西曆出生 年 月 日</span></span> 同 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">性別</span></span> <br />\n注明 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">檢查</span></span> 會優先處理 <br />\n<br />\n大家行街之前 有定心理準備 知所進退 <br />\n<br />\n當然其他問題亦一樣解答 <br />\n或直接Tg 詳見舊post <br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 我為你定方位 找好路 <br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad88f1fdcb8f31d5a3c72306ad8a237ac01cfba1","tid":1620091,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"1986年11月6日早上10點 男<br />\n會唔會有官非，冇官非問題今晚黑衫黑褲蒙面出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2811780f516c0be93d5f037642a93b04134776","tid":1620091,"uid":144447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:37:45.000Z","msg":"唔理你真心想幫定點都好<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好係到留個人資料，d狗抄低你出生日子同會員號碼就會易好多搵到你"},{"pid":"edadaab62113a836e0aeeefe8d8974c6130928e7","tid":1620091,"uid":268450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad88f1fdcb8f31d5a3c72306ad8a237ac01cfba1","tid":1620091,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"1986年11月6日早上10點 男<br />\n會唔會有官非，冇官非問題今晚黑衫黑褲蒙面出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmo